Before version 0.1
------------------

* Implement fetching of graphs
* Implement POSTing of SPARQL queries
* Implement of adding data from browser
  - Upload file
  - Form submit
  - HTTP fetch
* Implement some of SPARQL Update
* Implement adding/delete/updating of graphs using PUT/POST/DELETE
* Add more information about the store to the homepage
  - Storage name
  - Storage type
  - Storage options
  - Port Number
  - Total number of Triples
  - Number of graphs
  - Number of queries/requests
  - Uptime
  - Memory usage
* Return error messages to the client
  - internal error - eg memory allocation
  - query errors


